node.text:
Experience the best of life below the surface through the lens of a #GoPro. What's your all-time favorite? 

🔟 Exploring the Bahamas with #GoProFamily member @andremusgrove 🤿
9️⃣ #GoProAwards recipient @mathieuvillegas going below the surface of a frozen lake 🧊 
8️⃣ Observing the chaos of a sardine run with #GoProAwards recipient @expert.tours 🎣
7️⃣ Swimming in sharky waters with #GoProFamily member @abc4explore 🦈
6️⃣ Arctic Bear Productions sharing the sea with a family of polar bears 🐻‍❄️
5️⃣ Saving the turtles with @camerondietrich 🐢
4️⃣ #GoProFamily member @brinkleydavies takes us down under on the west side 🇦🇺 
3️⃣ Once in a lifetime whale diving with @deepleigh, @mandyraekrack, + Erin Magee 🐋
2️⃣ @orcaingrid + @orcaresearchtrust freeing an Orca whale caught in a fishing buoy 🐳
1️⃣ Surrounded by a million fish with William Mitchell 🤯

#UnderwaterPhotography #Sharks #NaturePhotography #Whales #Dolphins #MarineLife #Top10
